        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.16294v1",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-17T17:56:03Z",
        "description": "Recent simulations increasingly resolve the small-scale structure of the circumgalactic medium (CGM), but the dynamical impact of ionising radiation on its cold $10^4$ K component remains poorly understood. We investigate the evolution of cold gas structures exposed to quasars' EUV radiation. We dev",
        "title_cn": "冷环星系云对类星体辐射的流体动力学响应"
      },
      {
        "title": "Fast, High-Fidelity Erasure Detection of Dual-Rail Qubits with Symmetrically Coupled Readout",
        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.16292v1",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-17T17:54:23Z",
        "description": "Erasure qubits are a promising platform for implementing hardware-efficient quantum error correction. Realizing the error-correction advantages of this encoding requires frequent mid-circuit erasure checks that are fast, high-fidelity, and scalable. Here, we realize erasure detection with a hardware",
        "title_cn": "具有对称耦合读数的双轨量子位的快速、高保真擦除检测"
      },
