        "pubDate": "2026-04-17T15:40:09Z",
        "description": "The widespread dissemination of multimodal content on social media has made misinformation detection increasingly challenging, as misleading narratives often arise not only from textual or visual content alone, but also from semantic inconsistencies between modalities and their evolution over time. ",
        "title_cn": "MOMENTA ：多模态嵌入与神经时间聚合的专家混合，用于错误信息检测"
      },
